{"tid":1296421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突遭5名便衣警箍頸㩒地　廿歲仔慘被扭甩手骹","createTime":"2019-07-08T11:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T11:22:17.000Z","uid":20933,"like":594,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"2e78f32776bdaed0b756e1e78655d2f4705d4b54","tid":1296421,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:14:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190707/large/1562514302_26bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190707%2Flarge%2F1562514302_26bf.jpg&h=e143d73c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方昨晚於旺角彌敦道驅散示威者期間，有多名讀者拍到警方如何驅散示威者，其中一條讀者提供的片段中，見到10多名戴頭盔、身穿黑色背心的便衣警員與一名年約廿歲、孭背囊的男子在亞皆老街與西洋菜南街的交界位置拉扯，其間一名身型高大的便衣警員向男子呼喝，未幾有大約5名身穿黑色背心的便衣警員上前箍頸，嘗試將男子制服，但男子不停反抗，在現場的市民亦高呼：「警察打人呀」。"},{"pid":"34354c09da49bafb2bdc4c83d4497c98bba0455a","tid":1296421,"uid":20933,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:14:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190708/59799252\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190708%2F59799252&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpcjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=37ffff86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190708%2F59799252&h=85970593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190708/59799252</a>"},{"pid":"e1f17051b43c882011ce972240c4a7d20d12f55d","tid":1296421,"uid":92448,"like":183,"dislike":2,"score":181,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:14:31.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"9a58e2ac23609ed5ba757fdfe4bb33d10e2da52c","tid":1296421,"uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a07c312363f208abf5094094b4d9b668c58734a8